{"tid":2414351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有片 有線前記者黃浩賢2019年採訪期間被警員稱呼為「黑記」","createTime":"2021-02-19T10:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T11:51:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03a9d6454c26b5bddf0f5cc0b60d043d46e9fdc4","tid":2414351,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"有片<br />\n有線前記者黃浩賢2019年採訪期間被警員稱呼為「黑記」<br />\nFeb 19, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G1vLZxo2UvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG1vLZxo2UvY&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=6c73ebb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G1vLZxo2UvY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.9K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n有線前記者黃浩賢2019年投訴有警員稱呼他為「黑記」，投訴警察課事隔15個月，本月證實投訴成立。<br />\n<br />\n前年9月8日，網民下午發起「香港人權與民主祈禱會」及遊行到美國駐港領事館，晚上在港島及太子等區發生衝突。片段顯示，當時4名速龍小隊警員走向記者群，有警員要求有線攝影師出示證件，又指「你攞出嚟我點樣打你呀」，在旁的黃浩賢回應指攝影師沒提過有人打他，理論期間有警員稱呼他為「黑記」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=b1f7ed5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com</a>"},{"pid":"5e6752399d4c90738965f9bec62f75504207df29","tid":2414351,"uid":305058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"狗都唔洗負責任架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf80cdbac950df9a5129106b59bbd46ef5c37475","tid":2414351,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"支持真相<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要再被左膠和右膠迷惑<br />\n生命體不承認自己是人類<br />\n逐出人類圈無需分裂顛覆<br />\n把一切組織關到人類的籠<br />\n共同維護人類安全及權益<br />\n堅決地實現人類偉大復興<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2412985/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2412985/</a>"},{"pid":"16c6fd2970fc9d93b96d5abcf82b0c577435ff